==Definition==

<b>triangle</b> (<i>noun</i>)
# (<i>mathematics</i>) A three-sided [[polygon]].
# (<i>music</i>) A metal [[percussion]] instrument suspended by a string and hit with a straight metal bar causing a resonant sound.
# A [[relationship]] between three people.  (''love triangle'')

